In [100]:
for k = 1:21

cv=idx(:,k);
omega=2*pi*31/length(cv);
beta = 20;
cvo{k}=frac(1,sqrt(2))*(wavetrans(cv,{3,beta,omega})); %Positive side
cvr{k}=cv-double(cvo{k});%Residual minus filtered version 

[f{k},sppo{k},snno{k}]=mspec(dt,double(cvo{k}),double(psio{k}),'cyclic');%Spectrum of filtered version
[f{k},sppr{k},snnr{k}]=mspec(dt,double(cvr{k}),double(psio{k}),'cyclic');%Spectrum of residual

%The next line returns the filter used by wavetrans
[psi{k},psif{k}]=morsewave(length(cv),3,beta,omega,'bandpass');

end

idx1 = 1:10:643;
idx2 = 10:10:643;

for i = 1:64
    u=real(cv(idx1(i):idx2(i),2));
    u=u-mean(u);
    v=imag(cv(idx1(i):idx2(i),2));
    v=v-mean(v);

    [a2,b2,theta(i)]=specdiag(mean(u.*u),mean(v.*v),mean(u.*v));
    [kappa(i),lambda(i)]=ab2kl(sqrt(a2),sqrt(b2));

end

    axes(h(i)),ylabel('Period (days)')
